video_title: The MOST powerful thing YOU CAN DO  #adviceoftheday #mindsetpodcast #motivation
transcript:
this is the most powerful thing I think
somebody can learn because when your
identity changes your actions change and
when your actions change your results
change which is what is inside of the
identity triangle inside of the book
identity flows into actions actions flow
into results results flow back into your
identity and it can become a
self-fulfilling prophecy whether that's
good or bad you are who you think you
are and you will become whatever you
think you will become
